er they do business   our industry coverage teams include consumer retail financial institutions financial sponsors healthcare industrials natural resources power  utilities real estate technology media and telecommunications  mergers and acquisitions our ma group delivers strategic advice and services to companies worldwide on their most challenging and complex transactions the global team works in partnership with our industry coverage bankers to provide unique insights expert tactical guidance and bestinclass execution to help clients grow and manage their businesses our ma capabilities cover the entire spectrum of strategic options including  acquisitions defense  activism divestitures exclusive sales fairness opinions joint ventures leveraged buyouts mergers restructuring special committee assignments spinoffs debt capital markets we are a leader in the investment grade fixed income markets and are perennially ranked among the top underwriters of fixed income securities worldwide our teams work with clients to develop and implement tailored solutions to their specific debt financing needs and collaborate with coverage bankers across sectors to originate and structure deals our capabilities span the spectrum of fixed income financing including bonds liability management loans securitised products equity capital markets barclays’ global equity origination franchise has a proven track record spanning initial public offerings followon offerings block trades and private placements as well as equitylinked products and share repurchases our equity origination bankers work with our corporate finance sector experts and syndication teams to originate structure and market transactions we pride ourselves on guiding issuers through the most challenging of market conditions at every step of the transaction leveraged finance we are a leading global arranger and underwriter of debt capital in high yield markets providing clients with strategic advice at each stage of debt issuance including origination structuring and syndication working closely with our risk management partners we provide comprehensive financing solutions for noninvestmentgrade clients across all industry segments through the use of leveraged loans high yield bonds bridge financing and mezzanine debt products risk solutions our risk solutions group provides the strategic and tactical risk management solutions to our clients to manage their exposure to all kinds of financial risks including rates fx and enterprise risk management our team is fully integrated with our industry coverage partners as well as our corporate bank to deliver seamless solutions to clients around the world feature video link  trends ma mega deals and tech ipos what’s the outlook for mega transactions and tech deal pipelines barclays’ top ma and technology media and telecommunications bankers give their insights on the sectors and macro trends to watch this year feature video link air liquide crosses the atlantic to grow air liquide’s acquisition of airgas expanded its market in the us overnight igniting growth and enabling gamechanging transatlantic opportunities see how we helped air liquide expand feature video link the dynamic and diverse chemicals sector ma banker jean de miramon has over  years experience in the chemical sector in this video he outlines the vital ingredients for growth through ma and gives us an overview of the chemicals sector today igniting growth with our clients cocreating the future with cisco shake shack’s appetite for growth helping the gym group get britain fit helping ck hutchison drive crosssector growth meet newell brands leading china eximbank into the euro market equity one merges to better deliver the goods helping press ganey grow to give more patients a voice parsys  parsys  parsys  parsys  parsys  parsys  parsys  parsys  parsys  related information our insightsview highlights of research from barclays macroeconomic market experts and analysts and other insigh